question: {title} {name} sold his {property} for ${price}. He paid the {fee1_name} fees that amounted to {fee1_percent}% of the selling price and also paid a {fee2_name} fee that is {fee2_percent}% of the selling price. He also paid ${loan} for the remaining loan amount on the {property}, and ${extra} for closing costs. {title} {name} used the net proceeds from selling the {property} to invest in stocks. The stocks gained 10% each year for two years. How much were {title} {name}'s net proceeds after two years?
